comments: Dinwiddie (BKN) blocks the driving shot attempt by Wiggins (GSW) and the ensuing body contact is incidental.
Claxton (BKN) takes a dribble upon regaining control of the ball, but immediately loses possession.
Claxton (BKN) grabs and pulls Looney's (GSW) jersey, impeding him in the post before he enters his shooting motion.
Curry (GSW) drifts away from Johnson (BKN) during the driving shot attempt and any contact that occurs is marginal.
Paul (GSW) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Kuminga (GSW) briefly places a hand at Bridges' (BKN) side and the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Kuminga (GSW) avoids making contact with Bridges' (BKN) shot attempt after it hits the backboard.  Kuminga makes contact with the backboard but does not cause the ball to take an unnatural bounce.
Dinwiddie (BKN) grazes Curry's (GSW) front during the drive and the contact is marginal.
Podziemski (GSW) legally contests Thomas's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Curry (GSW) legally contests Dinwiddie's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
